metadata.name: How could resident Evil not carry the virus
metadata.description:
With the shield gone, the train slows down until it stops on the platform, and mercenaries get off and look around.



The young man with black hair walked out first, but when he came to Wang Jue, he said softly, "You are the first one who has run naked through horror movies."



And Wang Jue is helpless smiled to the people around say: "I actually have to wear underwear......" Said also afraid that people do not believe, quickly opened and closed once.



The public has seen a leopard pattern male underwear......
